STR: you're not stronger than me. 
CON: you can't break me.
DEX: you aren't faster than me.

WIS: you don't understand more than me.
CHA: you aren't liked/feared more than me.

STR: I can break that!
CON: I can grit my teeth and keep moving.
DEX: I can make that jump!
INT: I know this one!
WIS: I feel this one.
CHA: I can convince you!
